Asset Service as Non Fungible Token Transfer Start
Phase1: Proof of Radar Data Service for Assets
Submits the Oauth Access Token for the Road Radar Signature and initimates its completion
Submits the hash of the consolidated data with Road Radar Signature as a proof ensuring the completion
After the final proof is submitted then the Oauth Access token of the data pool is submitted to the platfform
Phase2: Offchain Transfer of Road Radar Signature Acess Token
Offchain Worker submits the Oauth Access Token as a webservice request
Posting of the Oauth Access Token happens only when the proof of the Road Radar Signature is submitted on chain
Acknowledges the reception of the Oauth Access Token to the datamarket
Transfers the Oauth Access Token of the Road Radar Signature to the Vehicle as WebService
Acknowledges the reception of the Oauth Access Token for the Road Radar Signature to the datamarket
Phase3: Fund Transfer
Transfers the amount as a reward of the Road Radar Signature offered from the escrow account
Transfer condition needs the Radar_OEM to submit a valid Oauth Access token as well as the hash proof of the Road Radar Signature
Transfers the amount as a comission of Bid Facilitation process from the Escrow to the Vehicle_OEM
Phase4: Finalisation of Asset Service Transfer
Transfers the ownership of the Non Fungible Asset Service Token and finalises the Asset Transfer
Phase5: Review of Asset Service Transfered
Submits the review of the Road Radar Signature Asset Service transferred as Non Fungible Asset Token
Review of the Non Fungible Asset Token helps in valuing the fidelity of the actors.
Asset Service as Non Fungible Token Transfer End
